Package org.game.connect4

package org.game.connect4
The package serves as the starting point of the Connect Four API. It includes the ConnectFourInitializer and the ConnectFourGame.
  • Related Packages
    Package
    Description
    org.game.connect4.exception
    The package includes all the custom exceptions of the Connect Four API.
    org.game.connect4.model
    The package includes all the models used in the Connect Four API.
    org.game.connect4.util
    The package stores all the utility classes of the Connect Four API.
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    ConnectFourGame
    ConnectFourGame contains the core logic of the ConnectFour game and all the functions required to play the game.
    ConnectFourInitializer
    ConnectFourInitializer provides different ways in which the ConnectFour game can be initialized.
